{"sn2.21:0.1":"Samyutta Nikaya 2.21 ","sn2.21:0.2":"3. Nanatitthiyavagga ","sn2.21:0.3":"Sivasutta ","sn2.21:1.1":"Evam me sutam—","sn2.21:1.2":"ekam samayam bhagava savatthiyam viharati jetavane anathapindikassa arame. ","sn2.21:1.3":"Atha kho sivo devaputto abhikkantaya rattiya abhikkantavanno kevalakappam jetavanam obhasetva yena bhagava tenupasankami; upasankamitva bhagavantam abhivadetva ekamantam atthasi. ","sn2.21:1.4":"Ekamantam thito kho sivo devaputto bhagavato santike ima gathayo abhasi: ","sn2.21:2.1":"“Sabbhireva samasetha, ","sn2.21:2.2":"sabbhi kubbetha santhavam; ","sn2.21:2.3":"Satam saddhammamannaya, ","sn2.21:2.4":"seyyo hoti na papiyo. ","sn2.21:3.1":"Sabbhireva samasetha, ","sn2.21:3.2":"sabbhi kubbetha santhavam; ","sn2.21:3.3":"Satam saddhammamannaya, ","sn2.21:3.4":"panna labbhati nannato. ","sn2.21:4.1":"Sabbhireva samasetha, ","sn2.21:4.2":"sabbhi kubbetha santhavam; ","sn2.21:4.3":"Satam saddhammamannaya, ","sn2.21:4.4":"sokamajjhe na socati. ","sn2.21:5.1":"Sabbhireva samasetha, ","sn2.21:5.2":"sabbhi kubbetha santhavam; ","sn2.21:5.3":"Satam saddhammamannaya, ","sn2.21:5.4":"natimajjhe virocati. ","sn2.21:6.1":"Sabbhireva samasetha, ","sn2.21:6.2":"sabbhi kubbetha santhavam; ","sn2.21:6.3":"Satam saddhammamannaya, ","sn2.21:6.4":"satta gacchanti suggatim. ","sn2.21:7.1":"Sabbhireva samasetha, ","sn2.21:7.2":"sabbhi kubbetha santhavam; ","sn2.21:7.3":"Satam saddhammamannaya, ","sn2.21:7.4":"satta titthanti satatan”ti. ","sn2.21:8.1":"Atha kho bhagava sivam devaputtam gathaya paccabhasi: ","sn2.21:9.1":"“Sabbhireva samasetha, ","sn2.21:9.2":"sabbhi kubbetha santhavam; ","sn2.21:9.3":"Satam saddhammamannaya, ","sn2.21:9.4":"sabbadukkha pamuccati”ti. "}